ds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"type":"topic"}}}